Kenzo:

"They might need a medic after this is over" Kenzo said to himself, 
then ran out of the maximal base and transformed into his helochopter 
form and flew towards the battle field.


Quickstrike:

"Hey looky over there where that explosion was, I think their might 
be some fighting, lets go check it out" Quickstrike said to the 
predacon potrol and started to run towards the battle field.

Waspinator:

Waspinator saw the blasts "Ohhh, Waspinator see fight" he said and 
flew towards it.

Inferno:

His head was laying half buried in the battle field right where it 
had been left by Grimlock, his body was in the maximal base, his 
systems straining to keep him alive.

OOC: Do you nead the head or the body to revive someone?
